<p>In charge: The actress is the co-founder of consumer goods company The Honest Company, and has said she's determined for the brand to put 'honesty and transparency' first, because she believes customers expect brands to have those values 'embedded into the model'</p>

<p>'I believe the reason why consumers are choosing Honest over others is because we have those values, not in spite of, and another huge aspect of our business is that we give back.</p>

